snippet.title: Amaya's Lost Soul  - Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to AMAYA’s LOST SOUL. In this 2d Action Game you play as Amaya the daughter of an all and mighty great “CREATOR” the leader of the out raiders. You Amaya are tasked taking down a kingdom in this choice driven 2d action platformer. 

if Interested Here is the Link 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2119380/Amayas_Lost_Soul/
